# how to create the retinotopy map
Here with using a subjects from studyforest we can regenerate the retinotopy map
The complete data set with command can be downloaded from the link:
https://www.dropbox.com/s/alak8b4n2g81rrw/sub_01.zip?dl=0

follow the commands or create the FSFAST structure
For details see the Power Point presentation.


 some useful links 
retinotopy                    

      https://surfer.nmr.mgh.harvard.edu/fswiki/FsFastIndividualRetinotopyAnalysis
      
Flattening a surface  

      https://surfer.nmr.mgh.harvard.edu/fswiki/FreeSurferOccipitalFlattenedPatch
      
